FBIS3-50941 "drlat007_a_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Raul Castro Reassures Disabled Officer FL1001144994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1255 GMT 10 Jan 93 FL1001144994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Army General Raul Castro promised Lieutenant (Elmis Brooks Shivas) that he would continue to be an active officer of the Revolutionary Armed Forces, despite the accident in which he lost a leg trying to save four individuals who were trying to leave the country.
